Yesterday was a day to remember at the Texas Aroid Show! We not only had a fantastic time, but also got to meet and mingle with some truly inspiring folks. It was such a treat to finally catch up with Ryan, Kim, and Brian from @wildrootsnursery And a visit to Steve’s Leaves? Absolutely delightful! Their dedication and fervor for plants shine through, especially Ryan’s - it’s so contagious that I ended up adding a couple of Begonias to our collection. A heartfelt thank you to the entire team for warmly welcoming us and sharing your plant stories. Can’t wait for the next one! 🌱

Can’t wait to share all the awesome photos from the Texas Aroid Show with you guys! 📸 I’ll dive into them as soon as we’re back home tomorrow. But for now, gearing up for that 20hr drive. Road trip vibes, here we come! 🚗 

